title: Minutemen Scans Event Pack - X-Men: Messiah Complex
description:
X-Men: Messiah Complex


"No more mutants." With those few words, the once thriving mutant population plummeted to a mere 198, placing the species on the brink of extinction. But everything changes with the first mutant birth since M-Day, initiating a series of events that will change the X-Men forever.
